	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Fortification</h1>
	
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
		<div id="contentSub"><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">&#160;&#160;(Redirected from <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Stronghold&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="Stronghold">Stronghold</a>)</span></div>
		
		
		<div id="jump-to-nav"></div>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="Stronghold#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="Stronghold#p-search">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">Not to be confused with <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Food_fortification" title="Food fortification">Food fortification</a> or <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fortified_wine" title="Fortified wine">Fortified wine</a>.</div>
<div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Military defensive construction</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"Fort", "Fortress", and "Stronghold" redirect here. For other uses, see <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fort_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Fort (disambiguation)">Fort (disambiguation)</a>, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fortress_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Fortress (disambiguation)">Fortress (disambiguation)</a>, and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stronghold_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Stronghold (disambiguation)">Stronghold (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
